themselves in open court in expeditious fashion" under protection
afforded by the country's law and constitution.
</P>
<P>
Anwar was arrested Sunday under provisions of the act, sparking
demonstrations in Kuala Lumpur.
</P>
<P>
Earlier this month, Anwar was fired from his posts in the
cabinet and the ruling United Malays National Organization.
</P>
<P>
