<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 25 (Xinhua) -- The Chinese language edition
of New Britain authored by British Prime Minister Tony Blair was
released here today and will provide Chinese people with a better
understanding of the British leader prior to his October visit to
China.
</P>
<P>
The release of the book could not have been timed better,
according to remarks Blair made in a letter to Chinese
translators. He also expressed great satisfaction that his book is
available to a potential audience of 1.2 billion Chinese people.
