<HEADLINE> News Items from Asia-Pacific Desk of Xinhua </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, September 25 (Xinhua) -- Following are news items
from the Asia-Pacific Desk of Xinhua in Hong Kong Friday:

hke092501 -- Major News Items in Leading Australian Newspapers
