China's NPC delegation will be led by Qu Geping, China's most
prominent environmentalist and a member of the NPC Standing
Committee and chairman of the NPC Committee on Environmental and
Natural Resources Protection.
</P>
<P>
The conference was first held in Seoul in June of 1993. It has
set a goal of parliamentarians pushing governments of the member
countries to consider more environmental and sustainable growth
issues and promoting environment cooperation among developed and
developing countries.  
</P>
